            {
              "id": "sentences",
              "label": "句型",
              "labelEn": "Sentences",
              "color": "green",
              "items": [
                {
                  "text": "Bones are hard because they support our whole body.",
                  "hint": "骨头是坚硬的，因为它们支撑我们整个身体。",
