                  "imageUrl": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530026186672-2cd00ffc50fe?w=400&h=400&fit=crop&auto=format&q=80"
                },
                {
                  "text": "If we had no bones, we could not stand up.",
                  "hint": "如果我们没有骨头，我们就站不起来。",
